pageContext.analysis: Trump tweeted an image with an incorrect poll result from Fox News. The network later admitted that the poll in question listed Trump's approval rating at 43 percent; his unfavorable rating was 55 percent. The poll did show Trump earning 58 percent approval for his handling of the economy.
